{"tid":197571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"5歲哈七向爸爸碧咸獻香吻 場面溫馨","createTime":"2017-04-12T03:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T07:04:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"892e218130cfeb065c675741342c3efaf04ba7f0","tid":197571,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58ec28a57a903.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58ec28a57a903.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=769023dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國足球明星David Beckham與老婆維多利亞（Victoria Beckham）在拚第 4 胎時，終於迎來了家中唯一的小女兒Harper，從 2011 年 7 月誕生至今已經 5 歲大，不知不覺已經急速長高，初長成英式小公主的模樣，她與爸爸的甜蜜親子互動，更讓人想感受到碧咸家庭果然是娛樂圈第一模範家庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58eb8d75bd09b.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58eb8d75bd09b.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=d93deecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼碧咸這個月帶著家人前往洛杉磯渡假，沒有回鄉證的社民連立法會議員梁國雄表示成功取得一次性通行證，同時也為他 18 歲的大兒子布魯克林（Brooklyn Beckham）打點人生第一個刺青，另外他也帶著哈七和小兒子克魯茲前往當地昂貴的 Olive And June 打點造型，可以看見哈七個子長得非常快，已經超過爸爸的腹部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58eb8d752ae7b.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58eb8d752ae7b.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=8da934c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼同時碧咸也展現了什麼叫做「有女萬事足」的喜悅，維多利亞為老公拍下了女兒在星期天早晨獻吻爸爸的甜蜜畫面，讓網友直呼：「哈七太甜了！」、「每一次看到千雪的照片，都會好想要快點組成家庭！」可見貝克漢家庭的溫馨生活日常，對於推動一般民眾「想婚」也有很不錯的效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58eb8d765343f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58eb8d765343f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fa7a564f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼同時碧咸和維多利亞也花了更多時間陪伴小女兒和小兒子，在洛杉磯時特地帶哈七和克魯茲去體驗騎馬，依照這一個時尚家庭的財力，未來哈七要爸爸幫忙買一匹小馬肯定也不成問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58ec28900daaf.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58ec28900daaf.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=cefb8c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看看為人父母的貝克漢和維多利亞幸福看著哈七騎馬的模樣，確實能讓人感受到碧咸家庭親密無間的親子互動，讓網友笑說：「哈七上輩子可能拯救了全世界，這輩子才能夠投胎到這麼幸福的家庭！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58ec2891c2a20.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58ec2891c2a20.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=530a99ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5fb8ebe2f5251cf3e7b78ec57ba5f61f186a248","tid":197571,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"做show啫"},{"pid":"a5c304279584b8bee60e95fb0bc95618230c0a5f","tid":197571,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58ec28a57a903.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58ec28a57a903.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=769023dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國足球明星David Beckham與老婆維多利亞（Victoria Beckham）在拚第 4 胎時，終於迎來了家中唯一的小女兒Harper，從 2011 年 7 月誕生至今已經 5 歲大，不知不覺已經急速長高，初長成英式小公主的模樣，她與爸爸的甜蜜親子互動，更讓人想感受到碧咸家庭果然是娛樂圈第一模範家庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64602/58eb8d75bd09b.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64602%2F58eb8d75bd09b.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%